{{Quote|These files contain minimal data. Little that is of any use to us—only the ramblings of historical scholars speculating about the original inhabitants, before the Mandalorians swept through. None of the data is current.|Tenel Ka|<ref name="Young Jedi Knights: Diversity Alliance">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Diversity Alliance]]''</ref>}}
The '''Kuarans''' were the indigenous people of [[Kuar]]. Their species was wiped out between [[5000 BBY/Legends|5000]] and [[4000 BBY/Legends|4000 BBY]] when the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] [[Mandalorian Crusaders|Crusaders]] conquered Kuar.

